      "rationale": "Independent senior FEA analyst (not involved in model construction) reviewed all boundary conditions, contact definitions, material cards, and load application. Checklist-based review per DePuy Synthes FEA-QA-007. Two minor corrections identified and resolved prior to final runs. Gradation 2 achieved."
