      "rationale": "Validation uses the identical screw geometry, material lot, and test standard as the COU. Two independent laboratories provide geographic and equipment diversity. The validation scenario is the COU scenario (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending); no extrapolation required. Gradation 3 achieved."
