    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Model Risk Level 3 assessment. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is acknowledged; the sponsor has accepted this gap with a commitment to multi-angle testing in the next design iteration. All QoI comparisons satisfy pre-specified acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96; percentage difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as sufficiently credible to support the 510(k) submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
